===[[Pokémon Masters EX]]===
{{main|Marnie (Masters)}}
Marnie forms a [[sync pair]] with {{p|Morpeko}}, {{p|Grimmsnarl}}, {{p|Mawile}}, {{p|Toxicroak}}, {{rf|Galarian}} {{p|Moltres}}, {{p|Scrafty}}, {{p|Cinderace}}, {{p|Liepard}}, and {{p|Cyclizar}} in [[Pokémon Masters EX]]. Her Mawile is capable of [[Mega Evolution|Mega Evolving]], while her Cinderace is capable of [[Dynamax]]ing, and her Grimmsnarl is capable of [[Gigantamax]]ing. Marnie became a playable sync pair on February 26, 2021.

Marnie has also made notable appearances in the game's main stories, [[Legendary Adventures]] and the [[villain arc]].

